INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (84,'Dornsife','Art History','120',4,' Foundations of Western Art ','Mediterranean and European art and architecture presented in historical, cultural and social context that introduces art history as a discipline.',1);
INSERT INTO `course` (`ID`,`school`,`major`,`number`,`units`,`name`,`description`,`semester`) VALUES (85,'Dornsife','Art History','125',4,' Arts of Asia: Antiquity to 1300 ','An introduction to the major art forms and monuments of religious art in India, Southeast Asia, China and Japan from prehistory to1300.',1);
